lmn-lg-pull-6 flix-std-clmn-sm-6 flix-std-clmn-sm-pull-6 flix-std-clmn-xs-12 flix-std-clmn-xs-pull-0 flix_currys-fullwidth\">\n<div class=\"flix-background-image\"></div>\n<div class=\"flix-std-content flix-info-icon\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-title flix-info-title\" role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"4\">300 AirDry Dishwasher 60 cm</div>\n<div class=\"flix-std-title flix-mpn-title\" role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"5\">Natural drying with fresh air</div>\n<div class=\"flix-std-desc\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-p\">Our 300 AirDry Dishwasher finishes each cycle with a breath of fresh air, performing 3x better than closed-door systems. The door opens automatically during the drying phase using fresh air to get plates and cutlery completely dry.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flix-alternate-features inpage_selector_feature\" data-module=\"FM00002C\" data-modv=\"1\" data-modtarget=\"FM00002C-tlh3q\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-conta1ner-flu1d\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-Zigzag-feat flix-features-alternating\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-row flix-feat-table\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-clmn-lg-6 flix-std-clmn-sm-6 flix-std-clmn-xs-12 flix-feat-table-cell\">\n<div class=\"flix-background-image\"><img class=\"flix-img-responsive\" src=\"https://media.flixcar.com/modular/static/inpage/9/images/loading.gif\" srcset=\"https://media.flixcar.com/webp/synd-asset/Electrolux-275366473-PSEEDW18MPA00003.png\" alt=\"3x better drying with AirDry \" data-flixsrcset=\"https://media.flixcar.com/webp/synd-asset/Electrolux-275366473-PSEEDW18MPA00003.png 200w, https://media.flixcar.com/webp/synd-asset/Electrolux-275366473-PSEEDW18MPA00003.png 400w, https://media.flixcar.com/webp/synd-asset/Electrolux-275366473-PSEEDW18MPA00003.png 600w, https://media.flixcar.com/webp/synd-asset/Electrolux-275366473-PSEEDW18MPA00003.png 800w, https://media.flixcar.com/webp/synd-asset/Electrolux-275366473-PSEEDW18MPA00003.png 1000w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" /></p>\n<div class=\"inpage_selector