.com/modular/static/inpage/1307/images/document-icon.png 400w, https://media.flixcar.com/modular/static/inpage/1307/images/document-icon.png 600w, https://media.flixcar.com/modular/static/inpage/1307/images/document-icon.png 800w, https://media.flixcar.com/modular/static/inpage/1307/images/document-icon.png 1000w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" /></a>\n<div class=\"flix-document-text\">USER MANUAL_1</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"inpage_selector_specification\" data-module=\"FM00010D\" data-modv=\"1\" data-modtarget=\"FM00010D-kkb2j\">\n<div class=\"flix-header-bar flix-d-h2\" role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"3\">Specifications</div>\n<div class=\"flix-std-margin\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-row\">\n<div class=\"flix-std-clmn-lg-12 flix-std-clmn-sm-12 flix-std-clmn-xs-12\">\n<table class=\"flix-std-specs-table\">\n<tbody class=\"flix_post_specs\">\n<tr class=\"flix_post\">\n<td class=\"flix-d-h6\">Series</td>\n<td class=\"flix-d-p\">300</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"flix_post\">\n<td class=\"flix-d-h6\">Energy Rating</td>\n<td class=\"flix-d-p\">E</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"flix_post\">\n<td class=\"flix-d-h6\">Number of Place Settings</td>\n<td class=\"flix-d-p\">13</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"flix_post\">\n<td class=\"flix-d-h6\">Dishwasher Programs</td>\n<td class=\"flix-d-p\">160 Minutes|90 Minutes|ECO|Quick 30 Minutes|Rinse &amp; Hold</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"flix_post\">\n<td class=\"flix-d-h6\">Push Button Functions</td>\n<td class=\"flix-d-p\">Buzzer|Delay start 3h|Drying phase|Rinse aid|Salt</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"flix_button_block 1\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<h2>Electrolux 13 Place Integrated Dishwasher KEAF7200L</h2>\n<p><strong>Product Information:</strong></p>\n<p>Our 300 AirDry Dishwasher technology finishes each cycle with a breath of fresh air, performing three-times better than closed-door systems. The door opens automatically during the drying phase and air leaves plates and cutlery completely dry.</p>\n<p><strong>Three-Times Better Drying with Airdry</strong><br />\nThe new AirDry technology uses natural airflow to finish drying, for up to three-times better performance compared to closed-door systems. The door opens 10cm towards the end of the cycle, letting air circulate for superb drying results.</p>\n<p><strong>Easy Installation, Perfectfit</strong><br />\nWith PerfectFit Sliding Hinges, it’s never been easier to install your new dishwasher. The hinges accommodate all niche machine heights and even remove the need to cut the plinth. You can be confident that your machine will fit into your kitchen perfectly.</p>\n<p><strong>Quick and Efficient</strong><br />\nYour new time saver. When you have a light load, our 30-minute quick wash programme offers the perfect solution. And all without compromising on results. For the perfect washing result - fast.</p>\n<p><strong>Height Adjustable Upper Basket</strong><br />\nProvides more flexibility as bigger items can be loaded in the lower basket by raising the upper basket on one side, even if the basket is loaded.</p>\n<p><strong>Product Specification:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Construction type: Built-In</li>\n<li>Installation: Fully integrated</li>\n<li>Product Type: Full Width (60cm)</li>\n<li>Product Classification: Entry</li>\n<li>Installation Type: Fully integrated</li>\n<li>Panel colour: Black</li>\n<li>Door Colour: None</li>\n<li>Side walls colour: Rough zinc coated</li>\n<li>Type of timer min.: EDW503</li>\n<li>Push button functions: On/Off|Programme Selection|Delay Start</li>\n<li>Knob/Command functionality: None</li>\n<li>Number of programmes: 5</li>\n<li>Number of Temperatures: 3</li>\n<li>Dishwasher programmes: 160 Minutes|90 Minutes|ECO|Quick 30 Minutes|Rinse &amp; Hold</li>\n<li>Indicator programme: LED</li>\n<li>Indicators display: None</li>\n<li>Other Indicators: Rinse aid|Salt|Buzzer|Delay start 3h|Drying phase</li>\n<li>Height (mm): 818</li>\n<li>Width (mm): 596</li>\n<li>Depth (mm): 550</li>\n<li>Tub material: Stainless steel</li>\n<li>Heating element type of: Interheater</li>\n<li>Inlet Pipe Type: Aqua control</li>\n<li>Inlet hose length (mm): 150</li>\n<li>Water Supply: Cold or hot</li>\n<li>Anti-flood Device: Floating switch</li>\n</ul>\n<p>(SKU: 7332543782741)</p>\n<ul class=\"productinfo\">\n<li><span class=\"productinfoleft\">Model:</span>KEAF7200L</li>\n<li><span class=\"productinfoleft\">Barcode:</span>7332543782741</li>\n<li><span class=\"productinfoleft\">Manufacturer:</span><a href=\"https://www.seanhennessy.ie/index.php?rt=product/manufacturer&amp;manufacturer_id=41\"><img title=\"Electrolux\" src=\"https://www.seanhennessy.ie/image/thumbnails/18/94/Electrolux_logo_png-100679-57x57.png\" alt=\"Electrolux\" /></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
